sources.sass\\style.sass:
$small: 1024px

*  
    margin: 0
    padding: 0
body
    width: 100%
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1b1b1b, #3a3838)
    display: relative
    .container
        width: 1280px
        max-width: 1280px
        margin-left: auto
        margin-top: 50px
        margin-right: auto
        margin-bottom: 150px
        @media screen and (max-width: 1024px)
            width: 840px
            max-width: 840px
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
            width: 640px
            max-width: 640px
        @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
            width: 320px
            max-width: 320px
        .offer_slider
            display: flex
            position: relative
            .prev
                width: 40px
                height: 80px
                position: absolute
                top: 360px
                z-index: 2
                cursor: pointer
                @media screen and (max-width: 1024px)
                    top: 225px
                @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                    top: 165px
                @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                    top: 60px
            .prev:hover
                background-color: #000000
                opacity: 0.4
            .offer_slider-wrapper
                width: 1280px
                max-width: 1280px
                overflow: hidden
                z-index: 0
                @media screen and (max-width: 1024px)
                    width: 840px
                    max-width: 840px
                @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                    width: 640px
                    max-width: 640px
                @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                    width: 320px
                    max-width: 320px
                .offer_slider-inner
                    display: flex
                    transition: 0.5s all
                    .offer_slide
                        position: relative
                        h1
                            position: absolute
                            left: 100px
                            top: 100px
                            font-size: 64px
                            background-color: #ffffff
                            background-clip: text
                            padding: 0 10px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                                left: 70px
                                top: 50px
                                font-size: 44px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                                left: 70px
                                top: 50px
                                font-size: 44px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                                left: 30px
                                top: 20px
                                font-size: 16px
                        h3
                            position: absolute
                            left: 150px
                            top: 180px
                            font-size: 56px
                            background-color: #ffffff
                            background-clip: text
                            padding: 0 10px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                                left: 100px
                                top: 120px
                                font-size: 36px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                                left: 50px
                                top: 50px
                                font-size: 14px
                        img
                            width: 1280px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 1024px)
                                width: 840px
                            @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                                width: 640px   
                            @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                                width: 320px                               
            .next
                width: 40px
                height: 80px
                position: absolute
                top: 360px
                left: 1240px
                z-index: 2
                cursor: pointer
                @media screen and (max-width: 1024px)
                    top: 225px
                    left: 800px
                @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                    top: 165px
                    left: 600px
                @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                    top: 60px
                    left: 280px
            .next:hover
                background-color: #000000
                opacity: 0.4
.arrow-left.icon 
    color: #fff
    position: absolute
    top: 30px
    margin-left: 3px
    margin-top: 10px
    width: 32px
    height: 0px
    background-color: currentColor
.arrow-left.icon:before 
    content: ''
    position: absolute
    left: 10px
    top: -10px
    width: 20px
    height: 20px
    border-top: solid 2px currentColor
    border-right: solid 2px currentColor
    -webkit-transform: rotate(-135deg)
            transform: rotate(-135deg)
.arrow-right.icon 
    color: #fff
    position: absolute
    top: 30px
    margin-left: 2px
    margin-top: 10px
    width: 32px
    height: 0px
    background-color: currentColor
.arrow-right.icon:before 
    content: ''
    position: absolute
    right: 10px
    top: -10px
    width: 20px
    height: 20px
    border-top: solid 2px currentColor
    border-right: solid 2px currentColor
    -webkit-transform: rotate(45deg)
            transform: rotate(45deg)
.carousel-indicators 
    position: absolute
    right: 0
    bottom: 0
    left: 0
    z-index: 15
    display: flex
    justify-content: center
    margin-right: 15%
    margin-left: 15%
    list-style: none
.dot 
    box-sizing: content-box
    flex: 0 1 auto
    width: 30px
    height: 6px
    margin-right: 3px
    margin-left: 3px
    cursor: pointer
    background-color: #fff
    background-clip: padding-box
    border-top: 10px solid transparent
    border-bottom: 10px solid transparent
    opacity: .5
    transition: opacity .6s ease
.portfolio
    width: 100%
    background-color: #ffffff
    padding: 50px 0  
    .portfolio-container
        width: 70%
        max-width: 1280px
        margin-left: auto
        margin-right: auto
        display: grid
        grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr)
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr)
        grid-column-gap: 10px
        grid-row-gap: 2em
        @media screen and (max-width: 1024px)
            grid-template-rows: repeat(4, 1fr)
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
        @media screen and (max-width: 320px)
            width: 90%
        .content-block
            margin-left: auto
            margin-right: auto
            position: relative
            .photo-img
                cursor: pointer
                @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                    width: 240px  
                @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                    width: 124px         

.icon-zoom-in               
    color: #030303
    font-size: 24px
    opacity: 0.6
    display: none
.icon-show
    display: inline 
.icon-zoom-in::before
    position: absolute
    left: 170px
    top: 170px
    @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
        display: none
.modal-window
    width: 100%
    height: 100vh 
    display: none   
    position: fixed
    background-color: #000000bf
    top: 0
    left: 0
    justify-content: center
    align-items: center
    z-index: 20
    .modal-container
        width: 400px
        height: 400px
        position: relative
        @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
            width: 240px  
        .modal-photo
            cursor: pointer
            @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
                    width: 400px  
            @media screen and (max-width: 425px)
                    width: 240px  
.modal-show
    display: grid
.modal-none
    display: none
.icon-zoom-out               
    color: #030303
    font-size: 32px
    opacity: 0.6
    display: none
    z-index: 100
.icon-zoom-out::before
    position: absolute
    left: 250px
    top: 250px
    @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
       display: none        
.icon-show-out
    display: inline
